    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Course content is good and the faculty in itself is very skilled and qualified.",
          "name": "Krishnika Raman",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports days and playing sports is made a priority as well in this college which offered a good physical health",
          "name": "Krishnika Raman",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching i must say is amazing. The teachers make learning interesting. The only thing is that the science students do not get to enjoy the extra curricular activities. Every class has a projector because of which learning becomes more fun.",
          "name": "Shweta kulkarni",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The library system is also great, the library provide all kinds of books like knowledgeable, academic related and more.",
          "name": "Saniya Sutar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college provide lot seminar programs for students.",
          "name": "Saniya Sutar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty of college is pretty good because they answer to all the problems",
          "name": "Nasrin fatima",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The way of teaching of professors are very professional and they are regular they teach everything very easily to understand",
          "name": "Nasrin fatima",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The revisions that are conducted before exams which makes us clear about the concepts & ask queries.",
          "name": "Sejal Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "college campus is very good because there are so many flowers and plants around the campus that is the best thing far so",
          "name": "Shruti Santosh Bhosale",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The campus a bit small in size but it has not intervened with the course and other benefits the college provides.",
          "name": "Krishnika Raman",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The only sad part is that is it a bit far from the bus sop",
          "name": "Shweta kulkarni",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They don't organise events and picnics to enjoy",
          "name": "Nasrin fatima",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The way of teaching is very traditional as they use blackboard",
          "name": "Nasrin fatima",
          "course_tag_name": "BBA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure of the college is quite limited, and has been facing criticism for a while now.",
          "name": "Vineebha Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "However, I feel very at home at St Mira’s since all the staff is female and it creates a very safe, competitive environment for students",
          "name": "Vineebha Prasad",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some technical courses should be added in the curriculum to be ready for the industry like Advanced Excel,etc for each & everyone.",
          "name": "Sejal Pathak",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "not that clean and hygienic about the college campus teaching faculty is not cooperate with students sometimes",
          "name": "Shruti Santosh Bhosale",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ]
    },
